---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Coach Derrick Lim Case Study | Digital Strategy | Winston Koh" description="90-day digital strategy roadmap with ROI projections for a freelance sports coach. A case study in conversion funnel design and strategic proposals.">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="gem-hero" style="min-height: 60vh;">
        <div class="gem-hero-content">
            <p class="gem-micro">Project Case Study <span style="color: #64ffda;">//</span> Personal Branding</p>
            <h1 class="gem-headline">Coach <span class="gem-text-gradient">Derrick Lim</span></h1>
            <p class="gem-subhead">From "Where do I start?" to a complete 90-day digital strategy with ROI projections.</p>
            
            <div class="gem-stats">
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="stat-val">90</span>
                    <span class="stat-lbl">Day Roadmap</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-box">
                    <span class="stat-val">3x</span>
                    <span class="stat-lbl">Lead Pipeline</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE PROBLEM -->
    <section id="breakdown" class="gem-section">
        <h2>The Challenge</h2>
        <p>
            Coach Derrick Lim is a freelance sports coach with deep expertise but zero digital presence. Like many solo practitioners, he was stuck in referral-only mode with no systematic way to attract new clients.
        </p>
        <div class="gem-callout">
            <strong>The Blocker:</strong> No website, no content strategy, no idea where to start. Classic "paralysis by analysis."
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE SOLUTION -->
    <section class="gem-section">
        <h2>The Solution: Strategy-First</h2>
        <p>
            Instead of jumping straight to building assets, I delivered a <strong>Strategic Proposal</strong> that prioritized clarity over complexity:
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-top: 1rem;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem; border-left: 2px solid var(--gem-gold); padding-left: 1rem;">
                <strong style="color: var(--gem-text-bright);">1. Audience Mapping</strong><br>
                Defined target segments (busy professionals, parents, athletes) with tailored messaging.
            </li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem; border-left: 2px solid var(--gem-gold); padding-left: 1rem;">
                <strong style="color: var(--gem-text-bright);">2. Conversion Funnel Design</strong><br>
                Mapped the journey from discovery (social) → trust (content) → action (booking).
            </li>
            <li style="border-left: 2px solid var(--gem-gold); padding-left: 1rem;">
                <strong style="color: var(--gem-text-bright);">3. ROI Projections</strong><br>
                Provided realistic metrics based on industry benchmarks to set expectations.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- TESTIMONIAL -->
    <section class="gem-section" style="background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.05); border-radius: 12px; padding: 2rem;">
        <blockquote style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-style: italic; color: #ccd6f6; border-left: 3px solid #64ffda; padding-left: 1rem; margin: 0;">
            "The proposal blew me away. I went from not knowing where to start to having a complete 90-day roadmap with ROI projections. Professional, fast, and data-driven."
        </blockquote>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem; color: #8892b0;">— Coach Derrick Lim, Freelance Sports Coach</p>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="athena-cta-section">
        <h2>Need a Strategy Like This?</h2>
        <p class="subtext">I build roadmaps that convert complexity into clarity.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact">Let's Talk →</a>
    </section>

</Layout>

<style>
    .gem-hero {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .gem-hero-content {
        max-width: 800px;
    }
    .gem-micro {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #64ffda;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .gem-headline {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ccd6f6;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .gem-text-gradient {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #64ffda, #00bcd4);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }
    .gem-subhead {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #8892b0;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }
    .gem-stats {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .stat-box {
        text-align: center;
    }
    .stat-val {
        display: block;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #64ffda;
    }
    .stat-lbl {
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: #8892b0;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .gem-section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
    }
    .gem-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        color: #ccd6f6;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .gem-section p {
        color: #8892b0;
        line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .gem-callout {
        background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.1);
        border-left: 3px solid #64ffda;
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    }
    .athena-cta-section {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 4rem 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .athena-cta-section h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        color: #ccd6f6;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .subtext {
        color: #8892b0;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
</style>
